{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"43374-chunu-munu-the-corn-is-yummy","title":"Chunu & Munu: The Corn Is Yummy!","description":"Chunu and Munu help their father grow corn. Will they get to eat some, too?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Alisha Berger"],"illustrators":["Abin  Shrestha"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/43374-chunu-munu-the-corn-is-yummy"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99528/size3/f0a253ffcb86cbc4b8093efa33ded772.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99528/size6/f0a253ffcb86cbc4b8093efa33ded772.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79446/size6/92d060da9019b2b4787e2ddb72649644.jpg","text":"Chunu and Munu are walking.\nThey reach the corn field.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79447/size6/8871ec6c92e15ae6faa41b55d3369920.jpg","text":"Their daddy is in the field.\nHe is sowing corn.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79448/size6/1012267efff10a9d6cd282705aab52f0.jpg","text":"“Can we help you?”\nthe girls ask.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79449/size6/60a79e1ba1662797bd9c758f8a5fdc0e.jpg","text":"Father looks at Chunu. \nThen he looks at Munu.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79450/size6/45f1e91823006dc932b5cf5bc9ca9ccc.jpg","text":"\"Okay,\" Daddy says.\n“Come and help me.”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79451/size6/29f4b103e4c6e7db8a3958815a027d9c.jpg","text":"Chunu and Munu are happy.\nThey water the corn.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79452/size6/ca8169b0d8693d20a64440096af30886.jpg","text":"Weeks later, the corn begins \nto sprout.\nThe girls cheer and smile.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79453/size6/58afaf85e6715d4b48db150fe3b70621.jpg","text":"They weed the corn.\nIt is growing so well!","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79454/size6/33eb185ef6356deb1568fb61cb00a521.jpg","text":"A few weeks later...\nChunu says,\n“Look at the weeds!”\nMunu says, \n“Look at the grass.”","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79455/size6/a8d8a0a620d9ed293cc1484fae187bb0.jpg","text":"Chunu pulls out the weeds.\nMunu pulls out the grass.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79456/size6/280292f6f65da8e376dc38cb713e87f5.jpg","text":"The corn crop is happy.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79457/size6/df8f1cfdd991dbeb4c981001e9ad932d.jpg","text":"Chunu picks the cobs.\nMunu puts them in a basket.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79458/size6/91e116dbc5de49698633a16edb7cffb6.jpg","text":"The basket is full of corn!\nThe girls carry it all the \nway home.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79459/size6/db8b911f5e69e43d5c97679942800069.jpg","text":"Daddy roasts the corn.\nChunu and Munu eat it happily.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79460/size6/c018e6b7505070e38ad97a6a379368c0.jpg","text":"Chunu and Munu cheer,\n“The corn is yummy.\nVery yummy!”","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":148}}